<L>__{interior apartment night}
<A>__{group of bags huddled next to the door. not the go on vacation set, but the clothes to coffee maker moving out variety. rob stares at them, his face unreadable, his head gripped by a big pair boudokan headphones. we hear what he is hearing, something foreboding and upbeat at the same time. laura, rob's girlfriend, enters the room, and he immediately pulls the headphones off. she clocks him for a moment, catching him in what seems to be an old and repeated moment of nonpresence. she begins to heft the bags, rob goes to her, a little tardy for his big goodbye. laura begins to cry a bit.}
