<D>__{well stay for tonight, then.}
<A>__{laura shakes her head, lifts the last small bag, and backs out the door. a strap catches on a handle and the two of them wrestle with it a bit, while trying to keep the door open, until laura awkwardly disappears from view and the door shuts behind rob. he stays right there staring at the shut door for a long moment, listening to the fading sound of laura and her dragging bags.}
